node.text:
Join me on this extraordinary & elegant adventure in Iceland taking you to some of the most beautiful and astonishing landscapes I’ve ever seen: from the Black sand beach in Vik to Jakulsarlon Glacier Lagoon, to Geysir the famous Geyser and the valley of Thormstork crossing rivers with a Super Defender, meeting with the wild arctic fox and the horses galloping through the lands. If you don’t know where to go for your next adventure, this might give you an idea of where to go ... A video which was not finalised in my archives and which I never published going from a project to another, and here it is. A big thanks to my whole team and friends who worked with me on this very special journey 🙌🏻
• • • • •

There has been a game changer in the high technology field. #Samsung brings us #TheWall, world’s first modular #microLED 146-inch TV with a 0.8mm pixel pitch, a HUGE screen for #homes & #superyachts. A technology revolution delivering unparalleled and truly immersive visual experience: intense black and contrast, pure colors along with outstanding brightness. A mind-blowing image where each picture looks like an open window on the world as if you were immersed within every scene you watch: a true-to-life imagery due to superior color purity. 
I personally loved watching images on this screen and it is for sure the most incredible picture I have
seen in my life.

#SamsungTheWall will be on private display at Ideaworks Monaco showroom located 13 rue de la Turbie 98000 Monaco. 
For any inquiry or booking a private demonstration email sales@ideaworks.co.uk

Full story, photos and information about The Wall will be featured on our digital magazine #TomClaeren.com shortly.

🎁 Guys we are hosting an amazing competition with @rebelliontimepieces this weekend, with 3 prizes to win !

Me & @watchanish are going to race and you can vote for who you back to win on the Rebellion Timepieces Instagram page. 

We will randomly pick 3 winners among those who chose the correct Champion (I’m sure it will be me!)…and remember you must be following @rebelliontimepieces to enter.

Here are the prizes:

🥇1st prize : one Rebellion Timepiece Tour Auto Edition

🥈2nd prize: a pair of Sunglasses by Rebellion x Roland ItIen

🥉3rd prize :  2 VIP passes to a GT world challenge race with access to Rebellion VIP lounge 

The winners will be announced by Rebellion within 24h, good luck to you all !
